UID:65ij8p316os3gb9p6hhm8b9k6cq66bb1cpij0bb56oo3cc9ocop66cr1c8@google.com
CREATED:20160219T024215Z
DESCRIPTION:Hello everybody\,\n\nFIRST TIMES CAN PLAY NOW FOR 415 FOR THE F
 IRST NIGHT\, AFTER THAT THEY NEED TO JOIN US TO CONTINUE PLAYING.\n\nOR\n\n
 Five card Fridays (good for 90 days): $85\nUntil end of June: $228\n\nTo pl
 ay with us your skill level must be B/BB. Don't know what that is? Click he
 re.\n\nNEW PLAYERS:\n\nFor your security and the security of our players we
  conduct a brief test to see your skills. This will happen as soon as you c
 ome in. The test consist in setting\, bumping and passing the ball. If you 
 are an intermediate or advance player\, this test will be very easy. We req
 uired a certain level of skills to play with us. Games can be very fast and
  dangerous (for you and other players) if you don’t know your position of h
 ow to receive a spike. If your skills are low\, you won't be able to play w
 ith us.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\nCoed t
 eams compete 6-on-6\, with a 2-woman minimum.\n\nYou will play at least 5 g
 ames (minimum) per night.\n\nSCHEDULE\n\n8:30 pm: arrival\n8:45 pm: warm up
  & hitting ball over the net (setting up)\n9:15-30 pm: start playing games.
 \n\nWe also play 2 on 2 games! Let the coach know you are interested before
  we start playing.\n\nAt the end of the night\, for those of you who don't 
 want to play 2 on 2\, we socialized at a private room on our facility. If y
 ou are planning to join us after\, please bring food or beverage to share w
 ith everybody. Any questions? shoot me an email.\n\n-- We are an intermedia
 te/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\nNEW & RETURNING PLAYERS:\n\nFor your sec
 urity and the security of our players we conduct a brief test to see your s
 kills. This will happen as soon as you come in. The test consist of setting
 \, bumping and passing the ball. If you are an intermediate or advance play
 er\, this test will be very easy. We required a certain level of skills to 
 play with us. Games can be very fast and dangerous (for you and other playe
 rs) if you don’t know your position of how to receive a fast spike. If your
  skills are low\, unfortunately you won't be able to play with us.\n\n-- We
  are an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\n(Please note\, our tea
 ms are made from class participants – we do not play against other gyms).\n
 \nWe can't wait to see you.\n\nGeorge & Honza\n\nDetails: http://www.meetup
 .com/friday-night-vollyeball-games-and-more/events/225561866/
LAST-MODIFIED:20160219T024215Z
LOCATION:420 East 71st Street\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Newbie? Play for $15 (new players only). Limited space.
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
