DESCRIPTION:Fee:\n\nFive Fridays card: $85 (good for 90 days)\nor\nHalf yea
 r season: $93 \n\nTo play with us your skill level must be B/BB. Don't know
  what that is? Click here.\n\nNEW PLAYERS:\n\nFor your security and the sec
 urity of our players we conduct a brief test to see your skills. This will 
 happen as soon as you come in. The test consist in setting\, bumping and pa
 ssing the ball. If you are an intermediate or advance player\, this test wi
 ll be very easy. We required a certain level of skills to play with us. Gam
 es can be very fast and dangerous (for you and other players) if you don’t 
 know your position of how to receive a spike. If your skills are low\, you 
 won't be able to play with us.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (
 B/BB level)--\n\nCoed teams compete 6-on-6\, with a 2-woman minimum.\n\nYou
  will play at least 5 games (minimum) per night.\n\nSCHEDULE\n\n8:30 pm: ar
 rival\n8:45 pm: warm up & hitting ball over the net (setting up)\n9:15-30 p
 m: start playing games.\n\nWe also play 2 on 2 games! Let the coach know yo
 u are interested before we start playing.\n\nAt the end of the night\, for 
 those of you who don't want to play 2 on 2\, we socialized at a private roo
 m on our facility. If you are planning to join us after\, please bring food
  or beverage to share with everybody. Any questions? shoot me an email.\n\n
 -- We are an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\nNEW & RETURNING P
 LAYERS:\n\nFor your security and the security of our players we conduct a b
 rief test to see your skills. This will happen as soon as you come in. The 
 test consist of setting\, bumping and passing the ball. If you are an inter
 mediate or advance player\, this test will be very easy. We required a cert
 ain level of skills to play with us. Games can be very fast and dangerous (
 for you and other players) if you don’t know your position of how to receiv
 e a fast spike. If your skills are low\, unfortunately you won't be able to
  play with us.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\
 n(Please note\, our teams are made from class participants – we do not play
  against other gyms).\n\nWe can't wait to see you.\n\nGeorge & Honza\n\nDet
 ails: http://www.meetup.com/friday-night-vollyeball-games-and-more/events/2
 25561412/
LAST-MODIFIED:20160118T021845Z
LOCATION:420 East 71st Street\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:It's Friday night\, let's play!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
