 wag. Come get your rad Bluetooth speakers and a truly unique limited-editio
 n t-shirt designed just for this event\, so you can show everyone that you 
 were the first on the scene!\n\nDon't forget\, it's all happening at the St
 andard High Line (https://maps.google.com/maps?q=the+standard+high+line&rlz
 =1C1AVNA_enUS569US570&es_sm=122&um=1&ie=UTF-8&sa=X&ei=LbpBVI2yF8-YoQTG54KAD
 A&ved=0CAgQ_AUoAQ&output=classic&dg=oo) Room and Terrace (https:https://us2
 .admin.mailchimp.com/campaigns/wizard/confirm?id=2058201#//maps.google.com/
 maps?q=the+standard+high+line&rlz=1C1AVNA_enUS569US570&es_sm=122&um=1&ie=UT
 F-8&sa=X&ei=LbpBVI2yF8-YoQTG54KADA&ved=0CAgQ_AUoAQ&output=classic&dg=oo) on
  Wednesday\, October 29th at 7:00 pm .\nWe are very close to capacity\, so 
 please help us make this event a great experience for everyone by and confi
 rm or cancel your attendance by clicking on one of the buttons below:\n\n\n
 **\n------------------------------------------------------------\nI WILL AT
 TEND (mailto:ricardo@bemyapp.com?subject=Attending%20-%20Reimagine%20The%20
 Possibilites&body=Dear%20BeMyApp%2C%0A%0AI%20am%20excited%20to%20be%20there
 !%0A%0A-%20NY%20Tech%20Enthusiast)\nI CAN'T ATTEND (mailto:ricardo@bemyapp.
 com?subject=Not%20attending%20-%20Reimagine%20The%20Possibilites&body=Dear%
 20BeMyApp%2C%0A%0AUnfortunately%2C%20I%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20atte
 nd%20this%20event.%0A%0A-%20NY%20Tech%20Enthusiast)\nCheers\,\nThe BeMyApp 
 Team\n\n============================================================\nCopyr
 ight © 2014 BeMyApp\, All rights reserved.\nYou registered for the Wednesda
 y 10/29 event.\n\nOur mailing address is:\nBeMyApp\n26 O'Farrell St\nSuite 
 500\nSan Francisco\, CA 94108\nUSA\n** unsubscribe from this list (http://b
 emyapp.us2.list-manage.com/unsubscribe?u=7605d9f2f2cc8f3d1a43d7f54&id=55064
