CREATED:20150930T010450Z
DESCRIPTION:Hello everybody\,\n\nFull year season: $420\nHalf year season: 
 $235\nFive card Fridays (good for 90 days): $85\n\nTo play with us your ski
 ll level must be B/BB. Don't know what that is? Click here.\n\nNEW PLAYERS:
 \n\nFor your security and the security of our players we conduct a brief te
 st to see your skills. This will happen as soon as you come in. The test co
 nsist in setting\, bumping and passing the ball. If you are an intermediate
  or advance player\, this test will be very easy. We required a certain lev
 el of skills to play with us. Games can be very fast and dangerous (for you
  and other players) if you don’t know your position of how to receive a spi
 ke. If your skills are low\, you won't be able to play with us.\n\n-- We ar
 e an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\nCoed teams compete 6-on-6
 \, with a 2-woman minimum.\n\nYou will play at least 5 games (minimum) per 
 night.\n\nSCHEDULE\n\n8:30 pm: arrival\n8:45 pm: warm up & hitting ball ove
 r the net (setting up)\n9:15-30 pm: start playing games.\n\nWe also play 2 
 on 2 games! Let the coach know you are interested before we start playing.\
 n\nAt the end of the night\, for those of you who don't want to play 2 on 2
 \, we socialized at a private room on our facility. If you are planning to 
 join us after\, please bring food or beverage to share with everybody. Any 
 questions? shoot me an email.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (B
 /BB level)--\n\nNEW & RETURNING PLAYERS:\n\nFor your security and the secur
 ity of our players we conduct a brief test to see your skills. This will ha
 ppen as soon as you come in. The test consist of setting\, bumping and pass
 ing the ball. If you are an intermediate or advance player\, this test will
  be very easy. We required a certain level of skills to play with us. Games
  can be very fast and dangerous (for you and other players) if you don’t kn
 ow your position of how to receive a fast spike. If your skills are low\, u
 nfortunately you won't be able to play with us.\n\n-- We are an intermediat
 e/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\n(Please note\, our teams are made from cl
 ass participants – we do not play against other gyms).\n\nWe can't wait to 
 see you.\n\nGeorge & Honza\n\nDetails: http://www.meetup.com/friday-night-v
 ollyeball-games-and-more/events/225560980/
LAST-MODIFIED:20150930T010450Z
LOCATION:420 East 71st Street\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:It's Friday night\, let's play!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
