UID:fqmh7ao6krpg203csp63663m40@google.com
CREATED:20140119T220141Z
DESCRIPTION:Ciao a tutti\, siete invitati al nostro Aperitivo con amici. Po
 rtate uno o piu' amici e le vostre storie da raccontare! La partecipazione 
 è gratis\, e la consumazione è opzionale ma consigliata.\n\nYou are invited
  to our Aperitivo con amici. Bring your friends and stories to share! There
  is no participation fee\, and the event is cash bar.\n\nGrazie\,\n\nRiccar
 do & Walter\n\nDid you miss our last Aperitivo? Don't worry\, we've got you
  covered!\n\naperITube\n\nWatch our last Meetup event.\n\nSLIDE SHOW: June 
 11\, 2013\n\n<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/mVIy7BXc2IQ?rel=0" w
 idth="440" height="330" style="margin : 5px \; max-width : 700px \; max-hei
 ght : 700px"></iframe>  \n\nWant to connect on Facebook? - Click HERE\n\nHo
 w to find us:\nWe will be near the bar area near the entrance\; just ask ab
 out Italian Chat as you enter. Look for Riccardo.\n\nDetails: http://www.me
 etup.com/italian-chat/events/156692782/
LAST-MODIFIED:20140119T220141Z
LOCATION:48 East 12th Street\, Manhattan\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Aperitivo con amici
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
