 ally just wrote a relevant blog post today... http://blog.sephiroth.it/2014
 /09/16/why-its-hard-to-find-android-developers\n\nAnyway\, I gave him a qui
 ck overview and he'd be happy to try and help :)\n\nHope you guys are able 
