BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20150822T130000Z
DTEND:20150822T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260426T104533Z
UID:katejd91fl2vjaj9sp3o6s2k9s@google.com
CREATED:20150822T005936Z
DESCRIPTION:Welcome back everyone! Come <a>play</a> some <a>beach volleybal
 l</a> :) <a>Games</a> will be 4x4\, rotating 3 teams\, rally scoring to 15.
  \n\nThings to Know: Wondering what intermediate means? <a>Simply</a> put\,
  you know what second ball means\, and you can bump\, set and spike.\n\nOve
 r all you can receive a <a>serve</a> and get it to the setter\, reliably se
 rve  and hot the ball over the net.  \n\nHere is a <a>video</a> of the leve
 l of <a>play</a> we <a>expect</a> at the bare minimum . \n\nhttps://www.you
 tube.com/watch?v=1Nf4aM-hEzE\n\nBut this is how we think we play...\n\nhttp
 s://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zmfd9etbXGE\n\nWe are a fun and friendly group.
  Any arguments over calls will be a redo.\n\n• "Daria plays" are discourage
 d\, but you get one freebie.\n\n• Dancing between plays is allowed! \n\n• <
 a>Open</a> invites to drinks/ <a>lemonade</a> after the game :) Losers can 
 drown their sorrows. \n\n• Sorry guys no refunds on day of cancellations!\n
 \n• PLEASE LET US KNOW IF YOU ARE NOT GOING TO MAKE IT.  Two no shows = ban
  for a month. \n\nWhere is it?\n\nPier 25 is located by the <a>West Side Hi
 ghway</a> between North Moore St. and Harrision St. It's the first Pier nor
 th of <a>Battery</a> Park City.\n\nhttp://pier25.com/location/\n\nClosest <
 a>subways</a> are: Canal (A\, C\, E)\, Franklin St. (1)\, <a>Chambers</a> o
 n the (A\,C\, 2\,or 3)\n\nThis week we will be <a>playing</a> at an Interme
 diate <a>level</a>. Bumping and setting consistently\, and no carrying allo
 wed. If you are unsure if you are at the <a>required level</a>\, please <a>
 message</a> Joe and he will inform you if you can <a>sign up</a>. If you do
  sign up and are not at that level\, you will be asked to sit this one out 
 and refunded your payment. We will have an <a>open play</a> <a>meet up</a> 
 again next week. Thanks!\n\nDetails: http://www.meetup.com/NYC-Co-Ed-Volley
 ball-Bump-Set-Spike/events/224699227/
LAST-MODIFIED:20150822T010306Z
LOCATION:West St @ N. Moore St\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:4x4 Intermediate
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
