DESCRIPTION: have scheduled the job discussion for next week\, on Monday 08
 .10.2018 at 3 pm (Swiss\, CEST time).\n\nYou will find Pix4D at rue du Cent
 re 172 (3rd floor) - 1025 Saint-Sulpice : https://goo.gl/maps/Na7dJUwaR3D2.
 \n\nIf you come by bus\, there are 2 options: 1/ from Morges train station\
 , take the bus 701 in direction of Bourdonnette\, stop at Venoge Sud bus st
 op. 2/ from the metro Bourdonnette\, take the bus 701 in direction of Morge
 s\, stop at Venoge Sud bus stop. The building is in front of the bus stop.\
 n\nOnce you arrive\, enter in the building and take the lift on your left a
 nd go to the 3rd floor. You will then be at our office - ring and someone w
 ill open you the door.\n\nI give you the phone number of our office in Sain
 t-Sulpice\, just in case: +41 (0)21 552 05 64.\n\nPlease ask for my colleag
 ues once you arrive in the office.
LAST-MODIFIED:20191019T234755Z
LOCATION:Rue du Centre 172\, 1025 Saint-Sulpice\, Svizzera
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Colloquio Pix4d
TRANSP:OPAQUE
