CREATED:20221128T180655Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you an international living in Switzerland and/or just enjo
 y getting to know people from different places while playing a board game? 
 Feel free to join our diverse community in Zurich every first Friday evenin
 g of the month to meet new people and play a few of our 200+ board games. I
 t's gonna be fun. See you at our next meetup!\n\n**UPCOMING EVENT**\n\nIt's
  holiday season and at the last Games Night of this year\, we prepared some
 thing special. If you're down for getting to know some new people over food
  in a festive mood\, then mark next Friday in your calendar. So dress chic 
 and join the Games Night Gala! (Dress code: smart casual and up)\n\nTicket 
 prices are CHF 10.- (including food). You can either twint the amount to 07
 9 719 71 30 or pay cash at the entrance.\n\n**Important note**: Although we
 've never run out of food in the past\, it is served on a first-come-first-
 serve basis.
LAST-MODIFIED:20221128T180655Z
LOCATION:Hirschengraben 52\, Zürich\, ZH
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Games Night
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
