UID:6cs6acb461hm6b9gcos3eb9kcgpmcb9o6ss34bb2c5i64dr4cpj3ep35c4@google.com
CREATED:20160212T005240Z
DESCRIPTION:Hello everybody\,\n\nFive Fridays card: $85 (good for 90 days)\
 nor\nHalf year season: $93\n\nTo play with us your skill level must be B/BB
 . Don't know what that is? Click here.\n\nNEW PLAYERS:\n\nFor your security
  and the security of our players we conduct a brief test to see your skills
 . This will happen as soon as you come in. The test consist in setting\, bu
 mping and passing the ball. If you are an intermediate or advance player\, 
 this test will be very easy. We required a certain level of skills to play 
 with us. Games can be very fast and dangerous (for you and other players) i
 f you don’t know your position of how to receive a spike. If your skills ar
 e low\, you won't be able to play with us.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/adv
 ance group (B/BB level)--\n\nCoed teams compete 6-on-6\, with a 2-woman min
 imum.\n\nYou will play at least 5 games (minimum) per night.\n\nSCHEDULE\n\
 n8:30 pm: arrival\n8:45 pm: warm up & hitting ball over the net (setting up
 )\n9:15-30 pm: start playing games.\n\nWe also play 2 on 2 games! Let the c
 oach know you are interested before we start playing.\n\nAt the end of the 
 night\, for those of you who don't want to play 2 on 2\, we socialized at a
  private room on our facility. If you are planning to join us after\, pleas
 e bring food or beverage to share with everybody. Any questions? shoot me a
 n email.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\nNEW &
  RETURNING PLAYERS:\n\nFor your security and the security of our players we
  conduct a brief test to see your skills. This will happen as soon as you c
 ome in. The test consist of setting\, bumping and passing the ball. If you 
 are an intermediate or advance player\, this test will be very easy. We req
 uired a certain level of skills to play with us. Games can be very fast and
  dangerous (for you and other players) if you don’t know your position of h
 ow to receive a fast spike. If your skills are low\, unfortunately you won'
 t be able to play with us.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (B/BB
  level)--\n\n(Please note\, our teams are made from class participants – we
  do not play against other gyms).\n\nWe can't wait to see you.\n\nGeorge & 
 Honza\n\nDetails: http://www.meetup.com/friday-night-vollyeball-games-and-m
 ore/events/225561853/
LAST-MODIFIED:20160213T010007Z
LOCATION:420 East 71st Street\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:It's Friday night\, let's play!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
