UID:n5m1lrm9dcfbjrvq2i3tigr99o@google.com
CREATED:20150722T231238Z
DESCRIPTION:It’s no secret that great design rules digital product developm
 ent these days. Not only does your app need to be incredibly easy to use an
 d understand\, but it has to be absolutely beautiful\, too. Unfortunately\,
  this isn’t always something designers can do in a bubble\, without the gui
 dance of deep insights or data.\n\nThat’s where a great UX researcher comes
  in\, and one of the best in the biz is Becca Hare. Formerly of Foursquare\
 , Becca now heads up design research for one of the most beautiful and intu
 itive products in the game: Sunrise.\n\nAt our next meetup\, Becca will sha
 re secrets on how to use UX research thoughtfully\, efficiently\, and effec
 tively - helping designers make smarter decisions and enabling them to crea
 te an overall improved UX and pleasant experience for a product’s users. Sh
 e will also answer the age-old question: "Does my startup need a researcher
 ?!"\n\nThis is one you don’t want to miss.\n\nDetails: http://www.meetup.co
 m/Product-Secrets/events/224104577/
LAST-MODIFIED:20150722T231239Z
LOCATION:29 Little West 12th St\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:PS #11: Using UX Research Effectively\, with Sunrise's Becca Hare
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
