CREATED:20160609T044534Z
DESCRIPTION:The Mobile Forum is a one-day conference\, bringing together to
 p-calibre mobile developers to help solve the problems that we collectively
  face. Through small\, topic-focused discussion groups\, we aim to help eac
 h other improve our development processes\, and ultimately make better prod
 ucts.This forum will be focused on technology. Topics will include everyday
 \, practical challenges (ex: speeding up build times\; increasing testabili
 ty)\, and technical ones as well (ex: coding across platforms\; improving n
 etwork efficiency).This is a participatory\, community-driven forum\, and w
 e need you to contribute to make this a success. Bring your knowledge\, you
 r experience\, and your questions\, too! We each bring to the table a diffe
 rent set of solutions to challenges we all face — the goal is for us all to
  walk away with concrete\, actionable best-practices learned from each othe
 r. Join some of the top developers in mobile to help make our industry move
  even faster!
LAST-MODIFIED:20160624T125502Z
LOCATION:Crosby Street Hotel 79 Crosby Street New York NY 10012
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:NY Mobile Forum Hosted by Facebook & Instagram
TRANSP:OPAQUE
