DESCRIPTION:Lollipop is here!\n\nWith all the changes that the new update b
 rings us\, it's time to have a meetup about it. We'll have a couple of grea
 t talks\, open the door for some demos & plenty of discussion over beer & p
 izza.\n\nThe Applico team will walk us through a redesign exercise on Googl
 e Zeitgeist and the Touch Lab team will follow up with a talk on Android 5.
 0 (details TBD).\n\nKevin (Touch Lab president & meetup organizer) will als
 o have news about Droidcon NYC videos\, and we'll show Material demos after
  our talks. If you have any Material demos to show the group\, get in touch
  with Olivia to coordinate.\n\nDoors open 6:45pm. Thanks to Lexi for coordi
 nating venue & refreshments\, and Hired for sponsoring! \n\nAfterparty loca
 tion TBD.\n\nHow to find us:\n1st floor lounge\n\nDetails: http://www.meetu
 p.com/android-developers-nyc/events/217869132/
LAST-MODIFIED:20141111T185002Z
LOCATION:175 Varick Street\, ground floor lounge\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Lollipop is here!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
