DESCRIPTION:Beach Volleyball at Pier 25 in Manhattan. We'll be on court #1.
  \n\nWe will be playing 4 on 4 with 1 person on each side rotating on to th
 e court for a straight 2 hours of volleyball. (THERE WILL NOT BE A THIRD TE
 AM THAT SITS OUT)\n\nThe $15/person is to cover the cost of the court/occas
 ional ball replacements. \n\nIf you reserve and cant make it there will be 
 NO REFUND!!! \n\nWe are playing with beach volleyball rules: \n\n1) No voll
 eying when receiving the serve\n\n2) No volleying over the net\n\nPlease ke
 ep in mind that if your skill level is not adequate you will not be asked b
 ack.\n\nHow to find us:\nBeach Volleyball at Pier 25 in Manhattan\n\nDetail
 s: http://www.meetup.com/New-York-Volleyball-Meetup/events/224671001/
LAST-MODIFIED:20150822T005937Z
LOCATION:Pier 25 Hudson River Greenway\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:4 on 4  Beach Volleyball! (High Intermediate to Advanced Level)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
