DESCRIPTION:Hello everybody\,\n\nFull year season: $382\nHalf year season: 
 $199 \nFive card Fridays (good for 90 days): $85\n\nTo play with us your sk
 ill level must be B/BB. Don't know what that is? Click here.\n\nNEW PLAYERS
 :\n\nFor your security and the security of our players we conduct a brief t
 est to see your skills. This will happen as soon as you come in. The test c
 onsist in setting\, bumping and passing the ball. If you are an intermediat
 e or advance player\, this test will be very easy. We required a certain le
 vel of skills to play with us. Games can be very fast and dangerous (for yo
 u and other players) if you don’t know your position of how to receive a sp
 ike. If your skills are low\, you won't be able to play with us.\n\n-- We a
 re an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\nCoed teams compete 6-on-
 6\, with a 2-woman minimum.\n\nYou will play at least 5 games (minimum) per
  night.\n\nSCHEDULE\n\n8:30 pm: arrival\n8:45 pm: warm up & hitting ball ov
 er the net (setting up)\n9:15-30 pm: start playing games.\n\nWe also play 2
  on 2 games! Let the coach know you are interested before we start playing.
 \n\nAt the end of the night\, for those of you who don't want to play 2 on 
 2\, we socialized at a private room on our facility. If you are planning to
  join us after\, please bring food or beverage to share with everybody. Any
  questions? shoot me an email.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (
 B/BB level)--\n\nNEW & RETURNING PLAYERS:\n\nFor your security and the secu
 rity of our players we conduct a brief test to see your skills. This will h
 appen as soon as you come in. The test consist of setting\, bumping and pas
 sing the ball. If you are an intermediate or advance player\, this test wil
 l be very easy. We required a certain level of skills to play with us. Game
 s can be very fast and dangerous (for you and other players) if you don’t k
 now your position of how to receive a fast spike. If your skills are low\, 
 unfortunately you won't be able to play with us.\n\n-- We are an intermedia
 te/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\n(Please note\, our teams are made from c
 lass participants – we do not play against other gyms).\n\nWe can't wait to
  see you.\n\nGeorge & Honza\n\nDetails: http://www.meetup.com/friday-night-
 vollyeball-games-and-more/events/225561048/
LAST-MODIFIED:20151111T030210Z
LOCATION:420 East 71st Street\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:It's Friday night\, let's play!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
