 010000000B36B3AEEB7974647B9BBF6D74CD285CC
ATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;CN=alessa
 ndro.crugnola@gmail.com;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:alessandro.crugnola@gmail.com
CREATED:20190117T154619Z
DESCRIPTION:Hi Alessandro\n\nThank you for the interview. I send you the in
 vitation to meet the team next Tuesday. It’s in the same place as last time
  (your first interview)\, so I hope you’ll find us without any problems. Pl
 ease announce yourself at the reception so they can give me a call when you
  arrive.\n\nI’m trying to gather as many team members as possible\, so you’
 ll have the possibility to get a good impression of the people and the work
  environment here at SBB.\n\nRegards\nDominik\n
