UID:61ijge9kc5h3eb9mchh66b9k6lgj6b9o6os3cbb36os66dhpchhjadb26c@google.com
CREATED:20230608T104915Z
DESCRIPTION:**NEW**:\n\n* **Next** events on: **Friday 9.6** & **Saturday 2
 4.6**\n\n**Summary:**\n\n* What? **Fun** events for **meeting new & old fri
 ends** **without any specific reasons** (like common interests\, hobbies\, 
 genders\, age groups or countries)\n* Event is **taking place 100%\, rain o
 r shine**. If rain Frau Gerold's amazing staff will move us under the tents
 \n* Several "**People Connectors**" who will wear a hat and we will be obse
 rving and connecting people as needed. **Feel free to ask us** if you need 
 help\n* **30mins before event** we will post in the **comments** of this pa
 ge a bird-eye-view map with the **exact location** of the tables & how many
  people can fit under the tent in case of rain & photos of the "**People Co
 nnectors**"\n* **Christos** wears a grey hat (see [PHOTO](https://photos.ap
 p.goo.gl/fjjdtiq3n9VxBSLW9)) and will welcome you all & can also call him o
 n 0768175380.\n* You can connect with others by: simply **walking up to peo
 ple** and saying "Hi can I join?" OR asking support from "People Connectors
 " OR by playing **fun games** (read more below)\n* TIP: If you feel there i
 s too many people simply **choose a small group** of 2-3 people and say hi.
  You don't have to talk to everyone :)\n* Towards the end of the event\, gr
 oups form adhoc and people will go **partying/bars** \\- just ask around an
 d join in :\\)\n* If you love what we do and would like to help please msg 
 Christos\n\n**Detailed Explanation:**\n\n* **What/Why? Fun** events for **m
 eeting friends** **without any specific reasons** (like common interests\, 
 hobbies\, genders\, age groups\, etc). The event is as simple as that 🙂 No
 t an expat meetup. Not a drinks/party meetup. Not a dating event. **It is**
  **a fun** **social environment** outside family and work\, where we simply
  **meet and hangout** with **new** and **old** friends. For more info read 
 "What we're about" [here](https://www.meetup.com/wearetheconnectionspace/) 
 to understand what we **believe**\n* **Where?** "Frau Gerolds Garten" @ Ger
 oldstrasse 23/23a\, 8005\, Zürich. Super great location with great food and
  drinks! Also outdoors which is not noisy.\n* **Cost? Free** event. We dont
  profit in any way. Please tip the bar staff\n* **Who?** Wir wollen gerne m
 ehr **Schweizer/innen** dabei haben! Alle sind willkommen und die meisten k
 önnen Deutsch sprechen. This is not an expat event. **Everyone is welcome**
 ! Bring whoever you want\, we always got space! Love the randomness:)\n* We
  heard **many experiences** of people creating new friendships\, boy/girl f
 riends\, and even getting a job!\n\n**How connect with others?**\n\n* **Wal
 k & Connect:** respectfully walk to anyone you want and say hi :) You will 
 be surprised how ready for talking and how open everyone is\, as everyone i
 s in the same situation.\n* **Play & Connect:** bring your own **board/card
  games** OR simply pick any game available and **start a game table**! **Ga
 mes** available: Uno\, Cards Against Humanity\, Frantic\, Taboo\, Exploding
  Kittens\, Mafia\, Debatable\, etc and also **Connection Games** from [The 
 School of Life](https://www.theschooloflife.com/store/games-card-sets/) to 
 scientifically create deeper connections while having fun!\n* So we provide
  the space\, people\, games\, drinks\, food\, party and you simply decide w
 hat you want to do :)\n\n**Tips:**\n\n* 90% of people come **solo** \\- you
  can too\\! :\\)\n* **Co-organisers** will be there to help you to connect 
 with others\n* **If it feels hard to talk to others** **remember:** everyon
 e here is **friendly** and wants to meet people\, so just say "Hi my name i
 s xxx". If **need help** connecting come to Christos who will make discreet
  connections\n* **Respect & seek quality\;** if discussions are fun then co
 ntinue talking. If not talk to others. Its that simple:) Having fun with ne
 w and old friends should be your goal of the meetup :)\n* **Persist\;** tur
 naround is big\, people come randomly to each event so you never know which
  new or old friend you ll meet:)\n* **Photos**: If want your photos deleted
  message Christos\n\nLooking forward to fun & connection! 🙂
LAST-MODIFIED:20230608T104915Z
LOCATION:https://meetu.ps/e/M9BVj/g6Xjd/i
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:"Connection Space" simply meet friends🙂OUTDOORS @ FRAU GEROLD incl
 uding GAMES
