CREATED:20160110T013431Z
DESCRIPTION:Fee:\n\nFive Fridays card: $85 (good for 90 days)\nor\nHalf yea
 r season: $128 \n\nTo play with us your skill level must be B/BB. Don't kno
 w what that is? Click here.\n\nNEW PLAYERS:\n\nFor your security and the se
 curity of our players we conduct a brief test to see your skills. This will
  happen as soon as you come in. The test consist in setting\, bumping and p
 assing the ball. If you are an intermediate or advance player\, this test w
 ill be very easy. We required a certain level of skills to play with us. Ga
 mes can be very fast and dangerous (for you and other players) if you don’t
  know your position of how to receive a spike. If your skills are low\, you
  won't be able to play with us.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group 
 (B/BB level)--\n\nCoed teams compete 6-on-6\, with a 2-woman minimum.\n\nYo
 u will play at least 5 games (minimum) per night.\n\nSCHEDULE\n\n8:30 pm: a
 rrival\n8:45 pm: warm up & hitting ball over the net (setting up)\n9:15-30 
 pm: start playing games.\n\nWe also play 2 on 2 games! Let the coach know y
 ou are interested before we start playing.\n\nAt the end of the night\, for
  those of you who don't want to play 2 on 2\, we socialized at a private ro
 om on our facility. If you are planning to join us after\, please bring foo
 d or beverage to share with everybody. Any questions? shoot me an email.\n\
 n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n\nNEW & RETURNING 
 PLAYERS:\n\nFor your security and the security of our players we conduct a 
 brief test to see your skills. This will happen as soon as you come in. The
  test consist of setting\, bumping and passing the ball. If you are an inte
 rmediate or advance player\, this test will be very easy. We required a cer
 tain level of skills to play with us. Games can be very fast and dangerous 
 (for you and other players) if you don’t know your position of how to recei
 ve a fast spike. If your skills are low\, unfortunately you won't be able t
 o play with us.\n\n-- We are an intermediate/advance group (B/BB level)--\n
 \n(Please note\, our teams are made from class participants – we do not pla
 y against other gyms).\n\nWe can't wait to see you.\n\nGeorge & Honza\n\nDe
 tails: http://www.meetup.com/friday-night-vollyeball-games-and-more/events/
 225561404/
LAST-MODIFIED:20160110T013431Z
LOCATION:420 East 71st Street\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Volleyball\, Chicken Tikka Masala & Slovak Sausage!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
