UID:409es6ea0hh2gl1pprtudhdfi0@google.com
CREATED:20150921T103829Z
DESCRIPTION:The #1 topic request we’ve gotten lately from Product Secrets m
 embers is GROWTH: that illusive beast which is the only metric that matters
  when you're trying to determine whether or not your product is working. Mi
 ke and Maya (the two people who run this meetup) both just started brand ne
 w companies\, so this is something we’re thinking a lot about too.\n\nHappi
 ly\, we were lucky enough to meet Maud Pasturaud\, who is currently VP of G
 rowth at Spring (and formerly Head of Growth at Secret and Head of Mobile G
 rowth at Gilt Groupe). Unlike most “growth hackers”\, Maud subscribes to th
 e growth method we agree is best for users in the long run: listen to what 
 people want\, build an awesome product\, get it in front of the right audie
 nce\, and growth will come.\n\nJoin us on Monday\, September 21st for an in
 troduction from Maud on growth: what it means\, how it works\, how to get s
 tarted\, and how you can make the biggest impact for your company.\n\nDetai
 ls: http://www.meetup.com/Product-Secrets/events/225075027/
LAST-MODIFIED:20150921T103829Z
LOCATION:29 Little West 12th St\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:PS #12: Growth\, featuring Maud Pasturaud (VP of Growth at Spring)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
