DESCRIPTION:First off\, 4/10 and New Work City are subject to change.  Just
  putting this on the roster.\n\nWhat API\, tools\, and open source projects
  do you use?  Want to spread some skills?  Send me a couple paragraphs on w
 hat you want to present.\n\nI'm setting this up as every 2 months.  Will ad
 just based on interest.\n\nPresentation ideas:\n\nIntellij for Android\n\nA
 ction Bar Sherlock\n\nFoursquare\, Meetup\, Twillio\, etc\n\nCrash Reportin
 g tools\n\nMemory leaks with DDMS\n\nWhatever.  If its useful and you think
  the community should hear about it\, propose.\n\nYou can also send in thin
 gs you think should be presented but don't want to do it yourself. We can p
 robably find somebody to handle it.\n\nDetails: http://www.meetup.com/andro
 id-developers-nyc/events/112628062/
LAST-MODIFIED:20221220T235950Z
LOCATION:412 Broadway\, Floor 2\, New York\, NY
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Tool Lightning Talks
TRANSP:OPAQUE
